---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How St. John Biocare handles your personal and health information under the Data Privacy Act of 2012 (RA 10173).">
  <article class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:720px">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="lead">Your trust matters. This explains how we handle your information under the Data Privacy Act of 2012 (RA&nbsp;10173).</p>

      <div class="notice">This is a starting draft. Final wording should be reviewed by your Data Protection Officer / legal adviser before launch.</div>

      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <p>Only what you give us through our forms — such as your name, contact details, preferred center, and the message you send — so we can respond to your inquiry.</p>

      <h2>Why we collect it</h2>
      <p>To reply to you, arrange appointments, and provide the care and information you ask for. We do not sell your data.</p>

      <h2>How we protect it</h2>
      <p>We limit access to staff who need it and keep it only as long as necessary for the purpose you shared it for.</p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>You may ask to access, correct, or delete your information. Contact us and we'll help.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
